{"tid":1684813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook fan page 日本代購連線 係詐騙！大家小心！","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T13:35:44.000Z","uid":191571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2050a60f051bafc5a1abeb7a40b2af2241f6dcb6","tid":1684813,"uid":191571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:33:51.000Z","msg":"話說小弟當初見到佢有代購Monster Hunter隻錶，見到岩價佢又有成4萬幾個like就幫襯佢！點知惡夢就開始！一開始話隻錶賣$4200，要先俾$1500訂，跟住過左幾日叫我俾埋尾數$2700，都照俾哂，過左兩星期佢聯絡我話要俾多$1200代購費同郵費，我屌佢點解當初話$4200依家又要俾多$1200，佢解釋話$4200係隻錶既全數，代購費未計，我話咁唔要叫佢退錢，佢話買左冇得退！俾埋呢$1200就今日收到貨！好！照俾！結果今日佢又話要收多$1000先送貨，話係送貨人員人生安全保證金！哥一刻即刻醒左知中伏，係佢fan page留言叫人小心，佢係詐騙！結果佢del留言加block埋我！好彩有啲苦主見到我留言主動聯絡我！依家哥條仆街俾其他苦主踢爆埋就block哂其他人！我知你地可能會笑我on9！咁都信！但我開呢個post係唔想再有人中伏！如果同係苦主既你！非常樂意你聯絡我，大家一齊提供證據去拉鳩佢老母！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTV1bFu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTV1bFu.png&h=63ece614&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuoukyQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuoukyQ.png&h=690987e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tmr7dQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tmr7dQ.png&h=e28b5d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F9EHNb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F9EHNb.png&h=c59012e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZSu40x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZSu40x.png&h=19b974c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgnV0yX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgnV0yX.png&h=9c8f8a45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91r7d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91r7d0.png&h=871e3188&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kq7u40J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkq7u40J.p